>greet_prog 100~
  if ispc($n)
    mpechoat $n You flail about but continue to fall...
    mpechoaround $n $N plummets downward...
    mpforce $n down
    if rand(50)
      mpat $n mpechoat $n Right before you reach the ground, you crouch your legs, tuck in your right shoulder and roll into the impact!
      mpat $n mpechoaround $n $N falls screaming from above, does a hard roll on the ground and then comes quickly to $s feet!
    else
      mpat $n mpechoat $n You try to break the fall by rolling into it but all you succeed in doing is breaking BONES.
      mpat $n mpechoaround $n $N falls screaming into the room, hits the ground heavily, and then lies very still.
      mpat $n mpasound You hear a terrifying shriek followed by a wet thud.
      mpat $n mpdamage $n 32d33
      mpat $n mppose $n stun
    endif
  endif
~
|


